OL,3,CCommunity 'let down' by the closure of
OL,4,Ciconic cultural centre
OL,6,FEmma Bush, whose son normally has
OL,7,Fmusic lessons in the building was left
OL,8,Fin the dark about the closure.
OL,10,FShe said: "It's very frustrating and
OL,11,FI'm feeling quite anxious because my
OL,12,Fson has a music deadline tomorrow. He
OL,13,Fneeds the technical equipment that's
OL,14,Finside (the building), in order to
OL,15,Ffinish that project and have it
OL,16,Fmarked... and yet he doesn't know
OL,17,Fwhat's happening.
