OL,3,CCommunity 'let down' by the closure of
OL,4,Ciconic cultural centre
OL,6,F"It's not just the students who have
OL,7,Fbeen let down, it's the whole town
OL,8,Freally, because it's a venue where I
OL,9,Fgo to several theatre performances a
OL,10,Fyear. There's always bands on.. so
OL,11,Fit's an arts hub for the community and
OL,12,Fwe're losing yet another facility in
OL,13,Fthe town."
OL,15,FMerthyr Tydfil Leisure Trust run the
OL,16,Fservices that are held in Redhouse but
OL,17,Fthe building is owned by Merthyr
OL,18,FTydfil Housing Association (MTHA).
