OL,3,CCommunity 'let down' by the closure of
OL,4,Ciconic cultural centre
OL,6,FThe leisure organisation had been in
OL,7,Fdiscussions to transfer the business
OL,8,Fto the housing association but MTHA
OL,9,Fsaid they were no longer able to
OL,10,Fprogress with the transfer as it would
OL,11,Fput their financial sustainability at
OL,12,Frisk.
OL,14,FThe contract complexities are similar
OL,15,Fto those which confronted Aberfan
OL,16,FCommunity Centre which was recently
OL,17,Fsaved from closure at the eleventh
OL,18,Fhour.
