OL,3,CCommunity 'let down' by the closure of
OL,4,Ciconic cultural centre
OL,6,FChair of Merthyr Tydfil Council
OL,7,FGeraint Thomas said: "Unfortunately
OL,8,Fthe college had to move their students
OL,9,Fout of the Redhouse and they will have
OL,10,Fto carry out their exams in a
OL,11,Fdifferent building over the next
OL,12,Fcoming weeks and months until a
OL,13,Fresolution is resolved.
OL,15,F"It's such a dire state of affairs, I
OL,16,Fthink we should have a public inquiry
OL,17,Finto the whole of the leisure trust."
