OL,3,CCommunity 'let down' by the closure of
OL,4,Ciconic cultural centre
OL,6,F"We will support Merthyr Tydfil
OL,7,FHousing Association to get a
OL,8,Fresolution for the building, and a
OL,9,Ffuture for the building, while they're
OL,10,Fin dialogue with Merthyr Tydfil
OL,11,FLeisure Trust. It's just not an iconic
OL,12,FMerthyr Tydfil building. It's an
OL,13,Ficonic building for Wales. You know,
OL,14,Fit's the centre and heart of our town."
OL,16,FWhat makes the building so historic?
OL,18,FRedhouse Cymru was built in 1896.
