OL,3,CCommunity 'let down' by the closure of
OL,4,Ciconic cultural centre
OL,6,FThe Old Town Hall was originally the
OL,7,Fseat of local government, which
OL,8,Fincluded the council chamber,
OL,9,Fmagistrates court and holding cells
OL,10,Ffor remand prisoners.
OL,12,FAfter years of use as a civic
OL,13,Fbuilding, these services moved
OL,14,Felsewhere in 1989.
OL,16,FThis left the Old Town Hall vacant.
OL,18,FAfter a few years, the Old Town Hall
OL,19,Fhad private ownership and was used as
OL,20,Fa nightclub where it was vandalised
OL,21,Fand fell into disuse and disrepair.
