OL,3,CCommunity 'let down' by the closure of
OL,4,Ciconic cultural centre
OL,6,FMerthyr Tydfil Housing Association
OL,7,Fresolved to save the building and they
OL,8,Fpurchased the Old Town Hall in 2007.
OL,10,FRedhouse is a Grade II listed building
OL,11,F` in the heart of Merthyr Tydfil.
OL,13,FThe iconic centre re-opened to the
OL,14,Fpublic on St. David's Day 2014.
