OL,6,FIt went through an extensive #8
OL,7,Fmillion revival programme, which was
OL,8,Fsupported by the Welsh Government,
OL,9,FEuropean Regional Development Fund,
OL,10,FHeritage Lottery Fund & Merthyr Tydfil
OL,11,FCounty Borough Council in association
OL,12,Fwith Miller Argent.
OL,14,FDawn Bowden MS stated she had written
OL,15,Fto MTHA to see "what the future plans
OL,16,Fare for the Redhouse."
